<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Me</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .about-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 900px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            margin: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        .profile-picture {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 20px auto;
            display: block;
            object-fit: cover;
            border: 4px solid #007bff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .content h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .content p {
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .hobbies {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .hobbies ul {
            list-style-type: square;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .hobbies ul li {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        .footer p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        /* Responsive design for smaller screens */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .about-container {
                width: 90%;
                max-width: 100%;
            }

            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .profile-picture {
                width: 120px;
                height: 120px;
            }

            .content h2 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            .content p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="about-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>About Me</h1>
        </div>
        <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5c88c50af4e5316a44e9f34e/1561979748910-GK0D8TFBNG229SYQFDTO/1_6fmeCsyGpT2hWdWstsLwQQ.jpeg?format=750w"
            alt="Your Photo" class="profile-picture">
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Karan Jadhav</h2>
            <p><strong>Qualification:</strong> BTech in Information Technology</p>
            <p><strong>Hobbies:</strong></p>
            <div class="hobbies">
                <ul>
                    <li>Coding and creating web applications</li>
                    <li>Reading books and exploring technology</li>
                    <li>Traveling and photography</li>
                    <li>Playing sports like badminton</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <p><strong>Other Details:</strong></p>
            <p>I am passionate about full-stack web development and love solving complex problems with simple solutions.
                Currently, I am working on improving my skills in JavaScript, React, and Node.js. In my free time, I enjoy
                exploring new places and learning about the latest advancements in technology.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Created with ❤️ by Karan Jadhav</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
